description:
Tenmu was one of the four worker groups, led by http://anidb.net/ch97428 [Erya Uzruth], who volunteered to explore and investigate the http://anidb.net/ch95428 [mysterious tomb]. It consisted of four members, though it is better to think of it as Erya`s one man team as the other three were elven slaves from http://anidb.net/ch95438 [Slane Theocracy].
Source: Overlord Wiki
name: Tenmu
